Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.30,0:00:12.15,OP,,0,0,0,,在心灵的街道中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.67,0:00:18.50,OP,,0,0,0,,闪耀着希望之光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.10,0:00:24.70,OP,,0,0,0,,用虚幻的羽翼挥动着梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.40,0:00:30.95,OP,,0,0,0,,是你与我寻找的目标
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.27,0:00:47.47,OP,,0,0,0,,真理总是隐藏在眼中 蓝蓝的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.82,0:00:54.32,OP,,0,0,0,,我们要往何处去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.20,0:01:01.12,OP,,0,0,0,,俩人未来与现今的流浪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.42,0:01:06.75,OP,,0,0,0,,我们继续踏上旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.80,0:01:13.62,OP,,0,0,0,,永远的目标地 无止尽的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.97,0:01:24.62,OP,,0,0,0,,希望能不放手不断追寻 直到永远
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.21,0:01:40.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正当我们到处打探\N奈落的行踪的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.45,0:01:41.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路上遇见了三只小猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.82,0:01:44.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这三只猴子又聒噪又冒失
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.02,0:01:47.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这些可爱的小猴子\N正在到处寻找的是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.49,0:01:50.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们负责守护的\N猿神大爷的神体石像
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.33,0:01:55.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而最后在村子的\N腌菜缸里面找到了猿神大爷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.20,0:01:57.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说出了一段\N令人惊讶的一段话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.23,0:02:00.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说他曾经\N感觉到一股强烈的妖气
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.40,0:02:01.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朝丑寅方向飞去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.04,0:02:03.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且突然消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.37,0:02:06.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,错不了  那一定是奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.74,0:02:08.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丑寅方向…\N是指东北方向吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.84,0:02:10.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以走了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.58,0:02:15.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下子\N已经知道接下来该往哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.72,0:02:17.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目标是丑寅方向
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.72,0:02:24.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第89话 他和他之间的探病大战
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.93,0:02:28.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明早就该上路了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.70,0:02:34.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果现在是什么状况啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.44,0:02:37.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.57,0:02:39.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  你别那么任性啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.51,0:02:42.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又不是戈薇自己喜欢感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.94,0:02:44.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这点我又不是不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.08,0:02:48.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的对大家  很不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.68,0:02:49.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没有耽误到大家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.92,0:02:51.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正马上又要开始旅行了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.79,0:02:54.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家也需要\N一点时间准备准备呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.19,0:02:54.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.09,0:02:56.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要去打理一些道具才行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.39,0:03:00.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子戈薇这场病\N来得还真是时候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.56,0:03:03.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点都没错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.60,0:03:04.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你千万不要放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.87,0:03:05.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胡说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.63,0:03:07.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不赶快把病养好怎么行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.20,0:03:07.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.50,0:03:09.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都知道你很心急
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.14,0:03:11.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就不要再责怪戈薇了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.77,0:03:12.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.77,0:03:13.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.61,0:03:14.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去你的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.64,0:03:15.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.51,0:03:21.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又没有责怪她的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.42,0:03:24.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这小子真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.02,0:03:26.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果戈薇要安心养病的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.52,0:03:28.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最好还是避开犬夜叉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.52,0:03:30.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偏偏枫姥姥又不在家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.29,0:03:31.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真伤脑筋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.56,0:03:35.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烧得很厉害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.93,0:03:36.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.30,0:03:39.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要不要回家休息几天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.30,0:03:41.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.44,0:03:43.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们那边\N应该有很好的医生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.24,0:03:45.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说还有各式各样的药呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.37,0:03:47.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.08,0:03:49.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.38,0:03:50.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看我还是回家休养
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.75,0:03:53.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干嘛跟我们这么客气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.01,0:03:54.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.58,0:03:56.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇姑娘  我来背你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.08,0:03:58.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还好吗  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.65,0:03:59.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.02,0:04:02.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在打什么主意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.19,0:04:04.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有啊  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.90,0:04:09.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天还要再请一天病假
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.66,0:04:10.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.17,0:04:12.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次只是小小的感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.60,0:04:13.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以今天…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.77,0:04:16.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.21,0:04:19.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日暮篱同学今天又请假了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.27,0:04:21.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次好像是感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.98,0:04:22.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.98,0:04:24.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是感冒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.28,0:04:30.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样?没胃口吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.49,0:04:32.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么胃口
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.35,0:04:34.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系  我去煮点热饮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.72,0:04:36.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你配着药吃下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.22,0:04:37.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.23,0:04:41.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么久戈薇都没回来过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.80,0:04:43.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么一回来就感冒了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.80,0:04:45.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概那边的天气比较冷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.73,0:04:49.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看得好好休养几天才可以
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.74,0:04:51.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.57,0:04:54.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小小的感冒也要请假啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.81,0:04:58.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她以前\N不是老用一些罕见的病请假吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.65,0:04:59.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.58,0:05:01.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们说要不要一起去看她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.75,0:05:02.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去探病啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.82,0:05:04.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇这次既然是感冒\N应该会在家休息
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.82,0:05:06.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要住院吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.45,0:05:07.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.96,0:05:08.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.82,0:05:10.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久没有见到戈薇了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.32,0:05:11.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真的有点想她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.66,0:05:13.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们要去日暮同学家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.33,0:05:15.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北条同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.60,0:05:17.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说戈薇突然感冒了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.67,0:05:18.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.77,0:05:19.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感冒了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.60,0:05:21.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北条同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.47,0:05:23.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要不要跟我们一起去…\N是吗?得了感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.60,0:05:25.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底要不要跟我们去探病啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.77,0:05:26.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪里怪气的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.91,0:05:32.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,枫姥姥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.18,0:05:34.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千万别乱了方寸  利吉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.28,0:05:36.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,镇静一点就可以解决
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.05,0:05:37.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.99,0:05:40.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说实在的\N好久都没打过妖怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.49,0:05:41.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作一点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.79,0:05:43.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就因为犬夜叉他们不在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.62,0:05:45.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一定要加倍努力才行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.86,0:05:48.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.43,0:05:52.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家快射箭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.94,0:05:57.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,枫姥姥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.64,0:06:04.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你碍到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.31,0:06:06.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.02,0:06:13.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.22,0:06:14.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  是你啊枫姥姥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.96,0:06:16.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在这干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.96,0:06:19.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说\N最近有很多妖怪出来作怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.33,0:06:23.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村子里面的人\N被袭击得怕得不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.16,0:06:26.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是因为\N奈落突然躲起来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.97,0:06:28.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前奈落在\N这些妖怪都乖乖的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.97,0:06:30.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下还不趁机会出来作乱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.84,0:06:37.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活得不耐烦啦  死妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.06,0:06:50.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.76,0:06:54.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.56,0:06:56.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是特地赶来帮我们的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.20,0:07:00.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想他根本没想那么多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.27,0:07:08.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别挡着我  滚开
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.01,0:07:12.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭小子\N知不知道本大爷是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.38,0:07:14.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,管你是谁都一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.22,0:07:17.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老子今天有事\N一定要进这个泥沼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.52,0:07:20.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个泥沼\N已经是我的势力范围了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.89,0:07:23.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再敢罗罗唆唆\N我的脑袋会吃掉你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.09,0:07:26.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用脑袋吃掉我是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.90,0:07:31.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有本事吃吃看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.17,0:07:38.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.97,0:07:40.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.98,0:07:48.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.12,0:07:53.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行了  下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.69,0:07:57.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整个山谷\N全都是我的势力范围
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.00,0:08:09.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.14,0:08:11.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个瀑布…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.01,0:08:13.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少废话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.14,0:08:19.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你聋了是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.78,0:08:22.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,枫姥姥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.02,0:08:24.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖怪一直都没再出现耶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.39,0:08:28.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底躲到哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.93,0:08:37.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在那边干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.56,0:08:39.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得来了就顺便嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.80,0:08:40.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们来看我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.44,0:08:42.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.94,0:08:43.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还在发烧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.17,0:08:44.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有一点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.04,0:08:46.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鼻子跟喉咙觉得怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.71,0:08:47.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有一点点咳嗽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.44,0:08:49.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你的  一点点小意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.08,0:08:51.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.55,0:08:53.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算一点小感冒\N也不能够太大意喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.95,0:08:54.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.95,0:08:57.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不晓得你最近\N为什么这么常生病呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.45,0:08:58.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是耶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.82,0:09:01.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了\N那个他有没有过来看你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.46,0:09:02.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪个他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.46,0:09:03.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别装了  那个像太保的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.22,0:09:05.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他怎么会来看我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.96,0:09:06.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.06,0:09:08.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他果然一点也不体贴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.20,0:09:10.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是这样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.83,0:09:12.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那现在是什么情况嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.97,0:09:14.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你快点医好它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.17,0:09:17.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想他是住远了一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.57,0:09:19.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远了一点是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.84,0:09:21.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.34,0:09:23.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有个叫北条同学来看你喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.98,0:09:25.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北条同学?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.58,0:09:26.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北条同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.58,0:09:28.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.85,0:09:30.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北条同学  你怎么也来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.58,0:09:34.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一听说你感冒\N就想要来看你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.62,0:09:36.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过我一直很烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.49,0:09:41.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底我能够为你做些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.63,0:09:42.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.50,0:09:46.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只想到可以送你\N能够帮助恢复健康的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.07,0:09:48.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不嫌弃的话  这些是送你的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.64,0:09:49.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.07,0:09:51.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有  这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.74,0:09:53.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是可以保佑你\N身体健康的护身符
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.51,0:09:55.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过仔细想想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.78,0:09:58.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还其实这些都\N出自于你们家神社呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.58,0:09:59.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.71,0:10:01.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我们家的那些护身符\N一点用都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.25,0:10:02.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.88,0:10:04.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有  这个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.59,0:10:05.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是哑铃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.59,0:10:07.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想你最好\N多做一点运动锻炼体力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.39,0:10:09.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢…谢谢你喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.26,0:10:10.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.73,0:10:12.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有其他哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.13,0:10:14.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先请进来坐再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.40,0:10:25.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我问你们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.14,0:10:27.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.54,0:10:28.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇回家养病啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.14,0:10:29.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回家?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.31,0:10:33.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是想\N在家里应该比较适合养病
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.31,0:10:34.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我就叫她回去养病了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.68,0:10:37.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛不说一声就这样跑回去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.25,0:10:38.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个浑帐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.42,0:10:39.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害我好不容易…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.05,0:10:40.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.92,0:10:42.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是你把我扔在这里\N一个人跑到哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.62,0:10:45.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝  去你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.06,0:10:48.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干什么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.20,0:10:50.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少罗唆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.34,0:10:59.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来好好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.47,0:11:00.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是名产吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.84,0:11:02.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是  马上要出远门了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.58,0:11:03.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是准备路上吃的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.95,0:11:06.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想应该不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.22,0:11:12.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明记得收在这里头的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.45,0:11:14.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.86,0:11:17.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到啦找到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.46,0:11:19.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是我们日暮家代代相传
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.59,0:11:22.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以治百病的灵丹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.33,0:11:24.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总算让我找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.67,0:11:25.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  爷爷\N有了这瓶药
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.87,0:11:26.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信过了不久之后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.80,0:11:30.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇一定可以完全好起来的\N算了  管他的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.80,0:11:32.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小蚋让开\N太好了…找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.48,0:11:36.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.01,0:11:39.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.71,0:11:41.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.98,0:11:44.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕  闯出大祸了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.39,0:11:51.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.49,0:11:53.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇好一点了没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.13,0:11:55.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐她一直在睡觉耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.83,0:11:57.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在有好多人来看她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.73,0:11:59.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.73,0:12:02.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些男生都好大一阵骚动呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.20,0:12:04.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪亚由美太有魅力了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.01,0:12:06.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说这些了啦  绘理
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.84,0:12:09.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们班那些男生\N好像也常在讨论耶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.51,0:12:11.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.38,0:12:12.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.28,0:12:15.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些臭男生\N也会在背后说我们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.22,0:12:15.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.52,0:12:18.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  我想出去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.39,0:12:26.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真的追来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.39,0:12:28.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么追来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.93,0:12:30.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然追到戈薇家来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.53,0:12:32.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是  来探病的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.53,0:12:33.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的好体贴哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.27,0:12:35.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这么说啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.54,0:12:38.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然他什么都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.87,0:12:41.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇已经\N有男朋友的事都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.54,0:12:44.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过听说\N戈薇的男朋友很体贴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.05,0:12:45.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.68,0:12:46.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.55,0:12:49.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们现在在说的是我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.78,0:12:50.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.92,0:12:53.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是呢\N我们说的是戈薇…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.05,0:12:55.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来说好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.19,0:12:57.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  戈薇\N已经有个在交往的男朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.79,0:12:59.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊  不过连\N戈薇生病都没来看她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.33,0:13:00.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个很过分的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.56,0:13:03.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学校…\N大家感觉起来很快乐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.20,0:13:08.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.30,0:13:09.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,草太  什么事啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.07,0:13:11.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉哥哥来看你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.58,0:13:16.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.58,0:13:18.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么会来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.71,0:13:21.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有啊\N想看看你现在怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.58,0:13:22.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来探我的病啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.82,0:13:26.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁叫七宝跟珊瑚\N他们两个紧张兮兮的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.29,0:13:27.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.09,0:13:29.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了我还有谁能来看你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.22,0:13:30.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.46,0:13:32.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的已经好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.59,0:13:35.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是还有一点点在发烧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.83,0:13:37.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全身好像也没什么力气
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.60,0:13:44.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可别以为\N我是来带你回去的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.11,0:13:46.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也认为你应该好好休养
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.24,0:13:49.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在能回家休养最好不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.34,0:13:50.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊咧  已经走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.98,0:13:57.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日暮同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.39,0:13:59.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.26,0:14:02.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.32,0:14:04.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想说…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.99,0:14:08.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日暮同学\N你有没有什么烦恼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.40,0:14:11.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烦恼?你是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.13,0:14:12.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么特别的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.03,0:14:13.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.27,0:14:15.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我愿意当你的忠实听众
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.00,0:14:18.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者应该说  我希望…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.54,0:14:22.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管什么事\N你都可以跟我说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.14,0:14:25.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会尽我最大的努力帮助你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.01,0:14:28.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以换句话说  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.02,0:14:31.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我们能够交往的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.89,0:14:34.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会…啊咧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.56,0:14:38.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们猜这题会不会考啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.16,0:14:39.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对耶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.17,0:14:47.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.87,0:14:49.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天就要学力测验啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.94,0:14:50.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学力测验?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.54,0:14:54.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且这次考试结果\N是升学的参考指标呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.04,0:14:55.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,升学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.41,0:14:58.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没有来上课的这段期间\N有没有温书啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.31,0:15:01.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没温到什么书…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.05,0:15:03.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇真受不你耶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.02,0:15:05.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就连明天会不会来上学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.95,0:15:07.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你都不知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.39,0:15:10.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快告诉我\N出题的范围是什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.82,0:15:11.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.43,0:15:13.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还在生病不会想来考试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.56,0:15:14.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然要考了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.70,0:15:22.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日暮同学  你还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.54,0:15:25.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北条同学  你帮帮我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.54,0:15:30.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你果然是有什么烦恼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.11,0:15:32.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你帮我恶补好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.25,0:15:35.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撑不撑得住啊这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.08,0:15:38.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都没有休息
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.59,0:15:41.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自然科这个部分\N它的范围已经很明确了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.22,0:15:45.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只要把公式背好就行…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.46,0:15:47.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.09,0:15:49.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可不要死撑哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.93,0:15:51.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.87,0:15:53.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们继续吧  北条同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.37,0:15:58.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们先走了  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.87,0:16:00.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天真的很谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.24,0:16:02.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见  日暮同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.01,0:16:05.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你们帮了我这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.45,0:16:07.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.38,0:16:08.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有  没事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.98,0:16:09.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.08,0:16:10.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.08,0:16:11.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.62,0:16:15.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续加油
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.59,0:16:20.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.63,0:16:21.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.60,0:16:23.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个什么学校考试的\N真有那么重要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.26,0:16:24.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然重要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.50,0:16:27.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话又说回来  你感冒又没好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.63,0:16:29.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个什么鬼考试管他去的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.14,0:16:31.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就因为感冒好了要回学校
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.31,0:16:33.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以不用功的话就糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.24,0:16:34.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是先把感冒治好比较要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.14,0:16:36.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两样都同样重要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.94,0:16:40.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我说你现在\N赶快乖乖上床睡觉嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.65,0:16:41.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.41,0:16:42.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.32,0:16:44.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的很想回学校嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.92,0:16:48.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点出去啦\N不要妨碍我温书
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.66,0:16:49.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.62,0:16:52.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦  我知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.67,0:16:59.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真是个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.94,0:17:03.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇  现在觉得怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.37,0:17:05.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈煮了一点稀饭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.44,0:17:06.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你吃一点好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.94,0:17:12.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每样看起来都好好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.21,0:17:13.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个拿到外面去卖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.18,0:17:15.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该可以赚不少钱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.95,0:17:18.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我劝你们两个最好不要乱碰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.45,0:17:21.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,云母
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.39,0:17:26.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什么都没拿\N什么都没碰过哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.96,0:17:27.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.73,0:17:32.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.41,0:17:46.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  头痛死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.72,0:17:52.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉哥哥你不是走了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.49,0:17:54.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想借用一下你们家的炉灶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.49,0:17:55.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炉灶?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.49,0:17:56.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用瓦斯炉行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.70,0:18:06.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.27,0:18:08.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要补充营养就得靠\N肝脏  肝脏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.00,0:18:11.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狮子肝  鲤鱼肝  鸡肝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.24,0:18:14.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加上做药引用的草还有树根
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.01,0:18:16.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉哥哥\N你要吃这些东西哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.01,0:18:17.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是我吃啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.45,0:18:19.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.71,0:18:20.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.52,0:18:30.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.02,0:18:33.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  这是药
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.73,0:18:34.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点喝下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.76,0:18:35.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,药?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.46,0:18:39.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好臭哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.80,0:18:41.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喝下去包管你百病全消
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.04,0:18:43.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么感冒一定马上就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.78,0:18:54.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的好恶心…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.58,0:18:55.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍耐一下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.05,0:18:56.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,味道不是很好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.82,0:18:58.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是保证功效如神喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.55,0:19:00.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个药是你自己熬的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.32,0:19:00.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.29,0:19:02.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能够治得好病
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.56,0:19:04.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种怪味道我还能够忍受啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.36,0:19:09.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  这个药真的有用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.30,0:19:09.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.07,0:19:15.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咿  咿…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.30,0:19:19.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喝下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.01,0:19:22.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐把肝脏汤喝下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.78,0:19:27.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肝脏汤…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.12,0:19:32.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的耶  好像真的有效
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.72,0:19:34.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没骗你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.59,0:19:35.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.62,0:19:37.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没…没什么大不了的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.32,0:19:40.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过你居然还知道\N这种配药处方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.36,0:19:44.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前我老妈教的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.56,0:19:45.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.60,0:19:47.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你妈妈做给你吃过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.33,0:19:48.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  材料有点不太一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.60,0:19:51.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我老妈用的\N是放了很久的干货
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.31,0:19:54.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我用的是生鲜的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.38,0:19:57.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生鲜的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.24,0:19:59.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生鲜的什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.55,0:20:00.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生鲜的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.12,0:20:04.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总…总之效果很棒啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.85,0:20:06.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.35,0:20:08.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就跟你说不需要那么客气
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.42,0:20:10.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚对不起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.69,0:20:11.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就说没关系了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.36,0:20:13.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也赶快睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.13,0:20:21.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你念的是不是什么咒语啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.40,0:20:26.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是\N很久以前我老妈教我的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.87,0:20:27.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.16,0:20:52.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去上学了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.10,0:20:58.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.17,0:20:59.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天感觉怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.21,0:21:01.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全身都舒服多了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.68,0:21:04.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你的药很有效喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.41,0:21:06.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早就跟你说过会有效的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.21,0:21:07.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然好多了\N那我就可以去上学了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.18,0:21:09.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算要考试我也不怕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.19,0:21:15.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惨了  完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.46,0:21:17.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个时候出门\N一定会迟到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.93,0:21:20.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕连考试都赶不上了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.40,0:21:23.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点走  一定来得及
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.00,0:21:25.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你叫我快一点也…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.43,0:21:27.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去换衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.67,0:21:32.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下啦  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.44,0:21:34.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别再说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.44,0:21:36.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是想要赶上考试的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.22,0:21:44.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家早
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.49,0:21:46.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.69,0:21:47.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你感冒已经好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.72,0:21:50.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好的睡了一觉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.22,0:21:51.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在好像全都好了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.76,0:21:52.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,考试准备得怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.23,0:21:54.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正我尽全力就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.76,0:21:55.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是要这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.16,0:21:56.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起立
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.65,0:23:37.65,ED,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.47,0:22:20.15,ED,,0,0,0,,红红的太阳照亮一切
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.65,0:22:29.95,ED,,0,0,0,,也照遍过去和现在
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.05,0:22:39.20,ED,,0,0,0,,那些夕阳下的想象
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.47,0:22:49.20,ED,,0,0,0,,这颗心真的能承担吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.70,0:22:54.12,ED,,0,0,0,,告诉我什么办法才能
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.40,0:22:59.02,ED,,0,0,0,,活得比以前更开朗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.02,0:23:06.45,ED,,0,0,0,,这么做就算会让自己委屈
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.32,0:23:13.00,ED,,0,0,0,,要默默承受伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.00,0:23:17.17,ED,,0,0,0,,会失去一切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.57,0:23:24.47,ED,,0,0,0,,真正的歌仍会不断在我心中回荡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.92,0:23:34.47,ED,,0,0,0,,真正的歌才是我的路标
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.65,0:23:41.65,ED,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.49,0:23:49.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  犬夜叉哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.13,0:23:52.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问你一个男人之间的重大秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.50,0:23:52.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秘密?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.46,0:23:54.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么是恋爱\N噗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.93,0:23:55.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱就是永远吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.20,0:23:57.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛无缘无故问我这个
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.77,0:24:00.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我偷偷喜欢上小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.77,0:24:02.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇  这件事让你去解决
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.54,0:24:03.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心好了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.74,0:24:05.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了这个可爱的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.27,0:24:06.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么样都会想出办法来的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.24,0:24:11.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次回 犬夜叉\N草太大胆的爱情告白
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.78,0:24:13.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个问题\N简直比打妖怪还要棘手嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.40,0:24:18.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉宝典
